FBIS3-8497 "dreeu048_b_94001" FBIS-EEU-94-048 Document Type:Daily Report 11 Mar 1994 BULGARIA Prime Minister Undergoes Heart Bypass Surgery AU1103103094 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 1000 GMT 11 Mar 94 AU1103103094 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network Language: Bulgarian Article Type:BFN [Text] Government spokesman Raycho Raykov is on the line. Good Day Mr. Raykov, we have heard that the prime minister is being operated on at the moment. [Raykov] Yes, it appears your information is correct. This morning the medical team at the Lozenets Hospital of the Military-Medical Academy, where Prime Minister Berov is hospitalized, decided to perform a bypass operation. We expect the operation to end in about one hour. When the results of the operation become clear the Press Center will issue an official announcement. [Announcer] We will expect your announcement.
